data.description: Great investment! Approx. half acre near Walmart across from Lake Brenda. Home needs just a little tlc, but good bones. Upgrade refrigerator, range. Built in cabinets in dining. Large bathroom, good size bedrooms, separate dining, plus bonus room. Lots of windows. Bright rooms. Partial fence. Siding, New flooring throughout. Lots of room to grow. Large outbuilding for extra space, workshop or office! This property is priced to sell. Has lots of potential for use. Bring all offers. Seller is motivated.
